...and when it has:
![cc2](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6683515/9410436/dd4eac84-4828-11e5-9223-dd5b35b191c6.png)
Also, everything works as it should do when I use Layers/Nodes instead of Scenes, but I need using Scenes because of physics support.
I hope I'm not the only one having troubles with it, and this problem is already solved (I can't test it with 3.7 by now).

eg:
